{"tid":277981,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（燒炭勝地）長洲東堤小築再有燒炭，一男子亡","createTime":"2017-06-10T05:45:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-10T10:52:59.000Z","uid":29314,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a8e8fe743628541e7892de12adb65c288783447a","tid":277981,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T05:45:18.000Z","msg":"長洲東堤小築一個單位，今早11時43分，一名55歲男子被發現在單位內陷入昏迷，旁邊有燒炭痕迹，救護員到場證實他當場死亡，警方正展開調查。<br />\n<br />\n本周四，東堤小築揭發男女燒炭自殺案，兩名各有家室，分別35歲及29歲的「姊弟戀」情侶，各自離家後到長洲租住度假屋，邊飲紅酒服藥邊燒炭，同睡床上共赴黃泉。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n長洲東堤小築一個單位，今早11時43分，一名55歲男子被發現在單位內陷入昏迷，旁邊有燒炭痕迹，救護員到場證實他當場死亡，警方正展開調查。<br />\n<br />\n本周四，東堤小築揭發男女燒炭自殺案，兩名各有家室，分別35歲及29歲的「姊弟戀」情侶，各自離家後到長洲租住度假屋，邊飲紅酒服藥邊燒炭，同睡床上共赴黃泉。"},{"pid":"6300b6ebde23a57e60a860869814d7bbf51f82a1","tid":277981,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T05:46:44.000Z","msg":"詛咒"},{"pid":"460bcc24da53aac8b3cb134bd97085e76440552a","tid":277981,"uid":52006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T06:12:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>詛咒</blockquote><br />\n不如話D人想自殺就會揀果度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"862e2e9c054b52fd383be5eb658c1a321a7cfd3f","tid":277981,"uid":3302,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T06:14:12.000Z","msg":"我都想去果面自殺"},{"pid":"e14df0d21218f3232660e289dfca4b3352d2d97d","tid":277981,"uid":53568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T06:15:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a8935bc087f5d113d46ed26b175023193e78842","tid":277981,"uid":52949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T06:17:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41057188473873a884b8de3c01d711288113d8da","tid":277981,"uid